  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my grandparents had a big house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So part of it was used by the Russian high officers to-- they-- they brought their families down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they lived in-- in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they could do that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would requisition either part of a house or-- or half a house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had like two rooms in a house that they were using.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we-- we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They started packing and getting out of there fast, so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw the military activity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And basically, the activity was that the Russians running away, you know, running back east.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the German attack was so well-organized, and motorized, mechanized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and the attack was a surprise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Russia didn't-- didn't expect it at that particular time so that was very little-- there was very little resistance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It just moved fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- there was a feeling of fright.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the streets were empty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were Russian sentries stationed like in the center of the town to help direct traffic, and very, very serious and very stern.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember seeing a truck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, I shouldn't have been.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like at the center of town where the sentry was standing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No civilians were supposed to be in area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw a truck with a wounded Russian soldier-- young boy, maybe-- was maybe 18, 19 years old, and badly, badly hurt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was bandaged up, but you could see the blood all over him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the sentry stopped even that truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and then-- and then continued-- they were probably trying to figure out where to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a hospital in the area there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I'm not sure whether he went to the hospital or continued back east.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
